05/2007 till:31/07/2007\t\tcolor:Hayley\n  bar:Meav      \tfrom:15/09/2004 till:19/07/2005\t\tcolor:Meav\n  bar:Meav      \tfrom:23/08/2006 till:08/03/2007\t\tcolor:Meav\n  bar:Meav      \tfrom:11/04/2007 till:03/05/2007\t\tcolor:Meav\n  bar:Meav      \tfrom:29/06/2007 till:17/08/2007\t\tcolor:Meav\n  bar:Meav      \tfrom:15/01/2012 till:31/08/2012\t\tcolor:Meav\n  bar:Meav      \tfrom:01/08/2013 till:31/08/2013\t\tcolor:Meav\n  bar:Meav      \tfrom:06/03/2015 till:04/04/2015\t\tcolor:Meav\n  bar:Meav      \tfrom:01/08/2015 till:15/08/2015\t\tcolor:Meav\n\n</timeline>\n\n== Discography ==\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Title\n!Date of release\n!Media format\n!Region\n!Chart peaks\n|-\n| ''[[Celtic Woman (album)|Celtic Woman]]''\n| 1 March 2005\n| CD & DVD\n| International\n|USA: #53 <ref name=\":0\">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/298871/celtic-woman/chart|title=Celtic Woman \u2013 Chart history {{!}} Billboard|website=Billboard|access-date=2 May 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[A Christmas Celebration]]''\n| 3 October 2006\n| CD & DVD\n| International\n|USA: #35 <ref name=\":0\" />\n|-\n| ''[[A New Journey]]''\n| 30 January 2007\n| CD & DVD\n| International\n|USA: #4 <ref name=\":0\" /> \n|-\n| ''[[A Celtic Family Christmas]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/Celtic-Family-Christmas-Woman/dp/B001KMIZ22/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1322058611&sr=8-1 |title=Celtic Woman, The High Kings \u2013 A Celtic Family Christmas |publisher=Amazon.com |accessdate=10 March 2016}}</ref>\n| 14 October 2008\n| CD\n| US\n|USA: #89 <ref name=\":0\" />\n|-\n| ''[[The Greatest Journey]]''\n| 28 October 2008\n| CD & DVD\n| International\n|USA: #75 <ref name=\":0\" />\n|-\n| ''[[Songs from the Heart (Celtic Woman album)|Songs from the Heart]]''\n| 26 January 2010\n| CD & DVD\n| International\n| UK: #122 <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/110618cluk.txt|format=Txt|title=Update 18 June 2011 (week 23) : Chart Log UK|website=Zobbel.de|accessdate=10 March 2016}}</ref> \nUSA: