lieve (Celtic Woman album)|Believe]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://music.barnesandnoble.com/Believe/Celtic-Woman/e/5099995543123?itm=1&usri=celtic+woman+believe |title=Believe [B&N Exclusive Version&#93; by Celtic Woman &#124; CD |website=Music.barnesandnoble.com |date=24 January 2012 |accessdate=10 March 2016}}</ref>\n| 24 January 2012\n| CD & DVD\n| International (except Japan)\n|USA: #13 <ref name=\":0\" />\n|-\n| ''[[Home for Christmas (Celtic Woman album)|Home for Christmas]]''\n| 9 October 2012\n| CD, DVD & Blu-ray\n| International\n|USA: #43 <ref name=\":0\" />\n|-\n| ''Silent Night''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.christianbook.com/celtic-woman/silent-night/5099901559521/pd/cd59951 |title=Silent Night: Celtic Woman |website=Christianbook.com |date=24 December 2015 |accessdate=10 March 2016}}</ref>\n| 9 October 2012\n| CD\n| US\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Emerald \u2013 Musical Gems]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://secure.wttw.com/catalog/detail?productid=PEMERLC |title=Pledge |website=Secure.wttw.com |accessdate=10 March 2016}}</ref>\n| 24 February 2014\n| CD, DVD & Blu-ray\n| International\n|USA: #29 <ref name=\":0\" />\n|-\n| ''[[O Christmas Tree (album)|O Christmas Tree]]''\n| 21 October 2014\n| CD\n| US\n|\n|-\n|''Solo''\n|29 May 2015\n|CD\n|International\n|\n|-\n|''Decade: The Songs, The Show, The Traditions, The Classics''\n|July 10, 2015\n|CD\n|International\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Destiny (Celtic Woman album)|Destiny]]''\n| 23 October 2015\n| CD, DVD & Blu-ray\n| DE, International\n|USA: #60 <ref name=\":0\" />\n|-\n|''[[Voices of Angels]]''\n|18 November 2016\n|CD\n|International\n|USA No. 77<ref name=\":0\" />\n|-\n|''[[The Best of Christmas]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.celticwoman.com/shop/celtic-woman-the-best-of-christmas/|title=Celtic Woman \u2013 The Best of Christmas|publisher=Celtic Woman|website=celticwoman.com|access-date=8 December 2017}}</ref>\n|24 November 2017\n|CD\n|International\n| \n|- \n|''[[Homecoming \u2013 Live from Ireland]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=http