HgC |location=Westport, CT |publisher=Greenwood Press |isbn=978-0-313-34361-2 }}\n* {{cite book |last=Morgan |first=David Lee |year=2003 |title=LeBron James: The Rise of a Star |location=Cleveland |publisher=Gray & Co. |isbn=978-1-886228-74-0 |url=https://archive.org/details/lebronjamesriseo00morg }}\n* {{cite book |last=Pluto |first=Terry |last2=Windhorst |first2=Brian |year=2007 |title=The Franchise: Lebron James and the Remaking of the Cleveland Cavaliers |url=https://archive.org/details/franchiselebronj0000plut |url-access=registration |location=Cleveland |publisher=Gray & Co |isbn=978-1-59851-028-7 }}\n\n==External links==\n{{Sister project links|n=Category:LeBron James|commons=Category:LeBron James|wikt=no|v=no|b=no|s=no}}\n{{basketballstats|nba=lebron_james|bbr=j/jamesle01}}\n* {{Official website|http://www.lebronjames.com}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20130709135603/http://www.nba.com/draft2003/profiles/JamesLeBron.html NBA.com Prospect Profile: LeBron James]\n* [http://www.usab.com/basketball/players/mens/j/james-lebron.aspx USA Basketball \u2013 LeBron James]\n* [http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1819129_1819134,00.html 100 Olympic Athletes to Watch: 1. LeBron James]\n* {{youtube|Qmd_vOWQWx4|LeBron James' 61-point game vs Charlotte Bobcats}}\n* {{IMDb name|1429908}}\n* {{NYTtopic|people/j/lebron_james}}\n\n{{Los Angeles Lakers current roster}}\n{{LeBron James}}\n{{Navboxes|list=\n{{Mr. Basketball USA}}\n{{Naismith Prep Player of the Year Award}}\n{{USA Today National Basketball Player of the Year}}\n{{Gatorade National Basketball Player of the Year}}\n{{Gatorade National Athlete of the Year}}\n{{Morgan Wootten Player of the Year}}\n{{McDonald's All-American Game Boys MVP}}\n{{Jordan Brand Classic All-American Boys Game MVP}}\n{{2003 NBA Draft}}\n{{NBA NumberOne Draft Picks}}\n{{NBA Rookies of the Year}}\n{{NBA All-Star Game MVP Award}}\n{{NBA scoring leaders}}\n{{NBA MVPs}}\n{{NBA Finals MVPs}}\n{{Miami Heat 2011\u201312 NB